window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A.D. 1432 - The blood lines of six great houses come together in the greatest knight of them all. Prepare yourself for the beast. </p> <p>He bears the name of de Russe, but the bloodlines of six great houses converge in the greatest knight England has yet seen. As the grandfather of Gaston de Russe, the dark one, Sir Bastien de Russe beholds a great and terrible legacy - one that makes him both the target and the leader, the hunter and the hunted. His story is the most powerful of all. Greatness and darkness abide in the man known as the beast. </p>"; 
